hopobject.body: I enjoy travelling wirralsportsmedicine.com CBS did Cowher no favors by putting him in this spot. His Steelers connection left Cowher open to anyone accusing him of tilting toward the black and gold. Feeling sympathy pangs for Mike Tomlin, Cowher walked to the border of Pom-Pomville and stuck one toe over. His shilly moment came late in the fourth quarter. Cowher said the NFL has a history of teams like the Steelers, who came into the game winless, going through bad stretches.
